The "listlabels" macro currently allows to list labels either from the current space or from a another single space using the spaceKey parameter. It would be useful to extend this macro to allow multiple spaceKeys to be defined to fetch results from more than one space. This issue is related to [CONF-14663|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONF-14663], in which similar feature is being requested for the "popular-labels" macro.

