The #personal-info-sidebar used in personal spaces displays inconsistent behavior across browsers.  When opened the sidebar displays on top of content in Firefox and Chrome.  However, in IE it pushes the content down below the sidebar.  I suspect this behavior is due to IE's inconsistent support of z-index property.  However, this behavior is confusing for users, and we should enforce a greater degree of consistency across all supported browsers.

